Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This strange story began{\i0}\N{\i1}on a blistering hot day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had received an unexpected mail{\i0}\N{\i1}from an old acquaintance of mine,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the message was just this:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am at the meeting place of the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pao, the sender of the message,{\i0}\N{\i1}was an acquaintance of mine,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it didn't mean that we{\i0}\N{\i1}kept in touch all that well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I grew suspicious, and started to\Nresearch Pao's current whereabouts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say that Pao is one of the three{\i0}\N{\i1}greatest Feng Shui masters here on Mars.{\i0} {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when I found his whereabouts,{\i0}\N{\i1}he had already left this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you weren't the\None that sent me this mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who visits from\Nthe inauspicious back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive the word from the heavens,\Nand lead me to the sun stone... {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what the pa-kua told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you shooting?! {lead-out decreased by 2 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are disrespectful fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi of Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really close! {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there... Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, she's rather young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird one, hot dog bun, loved one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's his secret love-child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, she's rather old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Child, mild, wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting Pao's daughter\Nto be this old already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't remember, {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I met you once when\Nyou were this little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an acquaintance.\NIt's been 10 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But your father sure was unlucky\Nto be in a traffic accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way to Jupiter, there was a sudden\Nspatial fluctuation in hyperspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the "girlfriend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the "secret love-child?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet, why were you at the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody outside the family knows\Nhe got into an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am at the meeting place of the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao sent me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Can you help me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is the whereabouts\Nof the sun stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction, day, and time you arrived\Nwas the best combination for Feng Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're\Nsearching for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. About that, we will have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the boss feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it could be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't have any particular favors{\i0}\N{\i1}to repay to Pao or this girl,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I decided to help them for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were too many things that made{\i0}\N{\i1}me suspicious to leave it alone.{\i0} {link to next line?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did Pao send me mail{\i0}\N{\i1}right before his death?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do those words mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who were those guys that attacked us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there was something about{\i0}\N{\i1}this girl named Meifa as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This universe is made of three different Chis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the Chi of Heaven,\Nthe energy that comes from the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the Chi of Earth, the energy\Nthat comes from a planet's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly Chi of Magnetism, the Chi\Nthat organisms like ourselves produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi from organisms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The human body always\Nproduces a magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That magnetic field and\Nthe magnetic field of the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,react to one another to create energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Feng Shui is the\Ntechnology that reads the energies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of nature such as this to\Nuse them in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream. {extra lead-in}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Feng Shui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the same thing\Nas fortunetelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Other fortunetelling methods\Nonly predict or prognosticate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Universal Feng Shui has the\Npower to make the bad into the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you were a Feng Shui\Nmaster as powerful as my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized that I never spent\Ntime like this with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me point out that I'm not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I would be a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, that would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I can be an elder\Nbrother or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ICE cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that "Anzan" refers to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mountain Hotel Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.58,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,(Blue Dragon)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Byakko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.84,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,(White Tiger)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.11,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,(Black Turtle)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.57,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,(Scarlet Phoenix)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, the cross-zenith method!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun stone is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.\NThey're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle of lao-chu. I don't need a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you think we would\Ntell you that easily—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're from the Blue Snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} from a syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following us around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't tell you that\Neven if you killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was because we couldn't get Pao...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So they told us to get\Nthe recipient of his mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the low end so we\Ndon't know any more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My father... is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pao's words showed where this stone was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean Pao is still alive somewhere?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he want me to find this stone\Nand do something with it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like I created more{\i0}\N{\i1}mysteries instead of solving them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, I decided to check out{\i0}\N{\i1}this stone, which was our only clue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a piece of the moon from\Nthat Gate accident 50 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We Feng Shui masters call it the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absorbed the fluctuations\Nin time and space
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and conceals a tremendous\Namount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only think of it as a plain old rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how much would it be if we sold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're gonna smoke, go smoke outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You always smoke in here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning this into a\Nnonsmoking area starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, you're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship is {\i1}my{\i0} ship, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you gonna do with this stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what my father is thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ein! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The luopan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be... I took the magnet off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it! {9 frames but decreased lead-in}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nmy father owned a sun stone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the two stones are resonating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to show me the whereabouts of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why Pao made you\Nlook for this stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why my father\Nsent the mail to you, Mr. Jet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and not to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The more righteous a guy was in his youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the more likely he's gonna fall\Nfor a young girl later in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Guys are so clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My father
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was one that believed in Universal\NFeng Shui, but not other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So my mother left the house,\Nand took me along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was seven years ago... {4 frames extra lead-out}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my father was able\Nto find our whereabouts easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never even tried to look for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was my father targeted by those men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because he was\Nfriends with bad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who my father really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was the consultant for a syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao had leaked information to me about the syndicate, back when I was a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao already wanted out of\Nthe syndicate back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's impossible\Nfor someone who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,important syndicate secrets\Nto ever leave the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Pao was afraid that more\Nbad things would happen to his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you can confirm\Nit all when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No response.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be... I'm sure this is the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have guests? {extra lead-in}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, Faye, please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they {\i1}your{\i0} guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out if you don't\Nwanna die with this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What rotten luck of the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes it's good to act selflessly.{\i0} {Original: "Sometimes it's good to act without asking "What's in it for me?"."}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fairies who are going to\Ngrant the princess' wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmanned fighters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So these would be the seven dwarves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! They're trying to scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike! Come back here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, if we apply\Nlots of energy to that stone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we can draw out all the{\i0}\N{\i1}forces trapped inside it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an all-or-nothing plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blast this rock with your plasma cannon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great plan this is... {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like you made it in time, Jet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa... It's been a while.{\i0} {9 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao, you're in unstable territory.\NI can't approach any closer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know... There isn't any{\i0}\N{\i1}oxygen left in here anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sent you that mail because I wanted{\i0}\N{\i1}you to bring my daughter here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... you willed us to be here\Nlike this using Feng Shui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Pao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meifa is here now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because she {\i1}wanted{\i0} to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might be right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I was being too hotheaded...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's wonderful to see you one last time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I despised you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I don't know if it was a good thing{\i0}\N{\i1}or a bad thing that we took her along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In any case, this was how{\i0}\N{\i1}this strange case ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She went back to Mars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the smoking ban was lifted{\i0}\N{\i1}from the living quarters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, unchanging daily life{\i0}\N{\i1}has returned, just as it was before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One thing that has changed, though...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer read the fortunetelling\Npages in magazines.{\i0}
